China: Guangzhou Reports 44 Dengue Fever Cases
----------------------------------------------
Guangzhou Ai Wei Ban notes that up to 10 Aug 2003 Guangzhou reported a
total of 44 dengue fever cases.
The Guangzhou Information Times reports that a Guangzhou Ai Wei Ban
official said, based on recent years of Dengue fever trends, August and
September [2003] would be the peak months. In 2002, this period registered
1068 cases, accounting for 75 percent of the total cases for the year.
--
Jack Soo
<jack.soo@kyip.net>
