Date: Tue 12 Aug 2003
From: Marilda Milagres <milagres@fclnet.com.br>; via: LISAS
<lisas@lisas.org.br>
Source: CBN Anhanguera 1 Aug 2003 03:55 [in Portuguese, summarized by
Mod.JW]
<http://goiasnet.globo.com/diversidade/com_report.phtm?IDP=7392>

Brazil: Goias (Goiania)
-----------------------
Up to the end of July 2003, the Health Secretariat of the city of
Goiania had notified 1424 cases of dengue (206 confirmed) and 7 cases
of DHF. During the same period of 2002, 802 cases (658 confirmed) and
2 cases of DHF were notified.
A death from suspected DHF occurred on 7 Feb 2003 in the Tropical
Diseases Hospital, Goiania. The victim was 30 years old.
--
Marilda Milagres
<milagres@fclnet.com.br>
